Description
===========
libapn is a header based C++ library developed to study vectorial
Boolean functions including but not limited to APN functions.

Classes
=======
The following high-level C++ classes are available:
             function
             /     \
            /       \
           /         \
  linear_function   permutation
           |         /   |
           |        /    |
           |       /     |
 linear_permutation   involution

